sequenceDiagram
    participant IoT as IoT Simulator
    participant EdgeX as EdgeX
    participant FE as Feature Extractor
    participant IDS as Local IDS
    participant Client as FL Client
    participant Server as FL Server
    participant QI as QI Aggregator
    participant ML as MLflow/Grafana

    IoT->>EdgeX: Envoie trafic / événements
    EdgeX->>FE: Fournit lectures locales
    FE->>IDS: Transforme en features
    Server->>Client: Envoie modèle global
    IDS->>Client: Fournit poids locaux mis à jour
    Client->>Server: Envoie update locale + métriques
    Server->>QI: Demande agrégation QI
    QI-->>Server: Retourne nouveau modèle global
    Server->>ML: Envoie métriques du round
    ML-->>Server: Dashboard / tracking